好學理我負分都要比人繼續扣<br />\n你敢？你連續兩支煙都食吾*到啦<br />\n學我地？！算把啦 傻系"},{"pid":"ea3fa5561db718cacfd4abc52f9d24e2e1cc3597","tid":1090413,"uid":166127,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T17:01:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gCQ2JWM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgCQ2JWM.gif&h=2fd06548&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"10f1dff8c3823dabf6b73362a26a80d4a150644b","tid":1090413,"uid":74933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T17:19:45.000Z","msg":"菜菜緒唔係十一頭咩<br />\n佢好似係ig拍片量過<br />\n咁高點止9頭"},{"pid":"f363b31ed56a07273ce5b6e7d9542ffc624e42c4","tid":1090413,"uid":40904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"764e836d7cf7c60e993f385a465a5f41eab823f3","tid":1090413,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T12:27:18.000Z","msg":"在戲劇演出中反派角色是不可或缺的，雖然不討喜卻能有畫龍點睛的作用，更有許多人因演出反派被一罵成名。日本網站便針對1千位10至50歲的網友做調查，選出「最適合演惡女的女星」，冠軍由9頭身美女菜菜緒奪下。<br />\n<br />\n本為模特兒的菜菜緒因在《時尚惡魔》中飾演富家心機女走紅，之後又演出不少反派角色，成為觀眾心目中的「惡女專業戶」，不過菜菜緒私底下十分親切，深受粉絲喜愛，網友們也表示「即使演了很多壞人角色也不會討人厭」。亞軍則為澤尻英龍華，她因主演電視劇《一公升的眼淚》爆紅，以清純形象闖蕩演藝圈，但卻爆出無故擺臭臉，人氣開始往下掉，在討人厭排行榜上更是榜上有名，之後接下惡女角色讓人覺得說服力十足。<br />\n<br />\n42歲的小澤真珠得到季軍，她在《惡作劇之吻》中飾演琴子（台版為湘琴）的情敵受到矚目，接著在《牡丹與薔薇》中使壞讓人嘆為觀止。第4到10名分別為影后木村多江、小池榮子、艷星高岡早紀、收視女王米倉涼子、情色女王壇蜜、曾一舉奪得女主角和女配角獎的大竹忍與遠野凪子。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pk4fhYE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPk4fhYE.jpg&h=497d3498&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BX0VhYE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBX0VhYE.jpg&h=5f7e3ddb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u5sP6RZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu5sP6RZ.jpg&h=f7e1cd6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FuaFt5k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFuaFt5k.jpg&h=d0912851&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T18:04:26.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 對腳正到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61172585a747ada31a3e718d15ab0f5cb6b772f2","tid":1090413,"uid":21028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T18:07:55.000Z","msg":"雖然係整容 但我屌"},{"pid":"595b7c46c952fb43e66bb414d9d6f13dcb0d5922","tid":1090413,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T18:13:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fbb3961f5090b1449bcb99056662867339f2786","tid":1090413,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T18:57:38.000Z","msg":"惡之女幹部 拷問責 OO揸取<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f90895c257d87f9ee5142a0f9f5888f4b54c560","tid":1090413,"uid":189109,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T19:59:46.000Z","msg":"可唔可以連續食兩支煙先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔得就算吧啦傻閪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"891b131111c4ee9ac2670bb9c7a242f74c895d47","tid":1090413,"uid":135957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T20:10:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ccb8b5278005ad0db761fc9921a289f889690dca","tid":1090413,"uid":4950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T22:27:43.000Z","msg":"佢幾時會下海<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif